quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">What is PRESSIE?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;PRESSIE is a gifting app. We provide everyone with the ability to show their gratitude and support to their friends and family. Even to someone they have just met that has had a positive impact on their lives and wanted to send them a little token of appreciation.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">PRESSIE is a gifting app. We provide everyone with the ability to show their gratitude and support to their friends and family. Even to someone they have just met that has had a positive impact on their lives and wanted to send them a little token of appreciation.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;I got an SMS saying I received a gift on PRESSIE, how do I collect it?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">I got an SMS saying I received a gift on PRESSIE, how do I collect it?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Download PRESSIE with the link in the SMS, sign up with your mobile number, then tap \\&quot;notifications\\&quot;, there you\'ll see your gift and how to collect it.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Download PRESSIE with the link in the SMS, sign up with your mobile number, then tap \"notifications\", there you\'ll see your gift and how to collect it.  Still cannot find your gift?  Contact joy@pressie.com.hk for further assistance.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Who can I send my gift to?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Who can I send my gift to?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;You can gift to anyone! You can find your friends on PRESSIE from the Friend list ! All you need is their Mobile Phone Number to send a gift.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">You can gift to anyone! You can find your friends on PRESSIE from the Friend list ! All you need is their Mobile Phone Number to send a gift.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Can I send a PRESSIE gift to someone overseas?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Can I send a PRESSIE gift to someone overseas?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Yes, you can !! PRESSIE currently operates in Hong Kong, India and Singapore. You can send a gift to your friends from these stores if they reside in these country. Just keep in mind that you CANNOT send gifts to them from a store that they do not reside in, otherwise they wouldn\'t be able to redeem the gift.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Yes, you can !! PRESSIE currently operates in Hong Kong, India and Singapore. You can send a gift to your friends from these stores if they reside in these country. Just keep in mind that you CANNOT send gifts to them from a store that they do not reside in, otherwise they wouldn\'t be able to redeem the gift.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How do I send a gift?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How do I send a gift?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Choose the gift, tap \\&quot;PRESSIE It!\\&quot; choose the recipient from your contacts, add a message, checkout, and it\'s sent!&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Choose the gift, tap \"PRESSIE It!\" choose the recipient from your contacts, add a message, checkout, and it\'s sent!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How do I use a promo code?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How do I use a promo code?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;If you have a promo code, simply enter your promo code and tap \\&quot;Apply\\&quot; at the checkout page after you filled in your message, The promo code value should deduct from the final checkout amount. If you have any question on using a promote code, please email us at joy@pressie.com.hk&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">If you have a promo code, simply enter your promo code and tap \"Apply\" at the checkout page after you filled in your message, The promo code value should deduct from the final checkout amount. If you have any question on using a promote code, please email us at joy@pressie.com.hk</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How do I pay for gifts I send?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How do I pay for gifts I send?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Right now we only accept payment by Visa, MasterCard, and PayPal.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Right now we only accept payment by Visa, MasterCard, and PayPal.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;What would the PRESSIE gift look like?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">What would the PRESSIE gift look like?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Your gift will be shown in a form of QR Code or your friend will have to fill in the delivery form if that is a delivery gift. INSERT SAMPLE&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Your gift will be shown in a form of QR Code or your friend will have to fill in the delivery form if that is a delivery gift. INSERT SAMPLE.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Does my friend need the PRESSIE app to receive my gift?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Does my friend need the PRESSIE app to receive my gift?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Yes! Your friend will receive an SMS to notify them that you have sent them a gift. They can simply download the App and login with their mobile number to receive it !&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Yes! Your friend will receive an SMS to notify them that you have sent them a gift. They can simply download the App and login with their mobile number to receive it !</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;What if my friend failed to receive the PRESSIE gift?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">What if my friend failed to receive the PRESSIE gift?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;They must login PRESSIE App with the same number you sent the gift to. Simply email us at joy@pressie.com.hk if you have any question :)&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">They must login PRESSIE App with the same number you sent the gift to. Simply email us at joy@pressie.com.hk if you have any question :)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Where can I find all the PRESSIE gifts I sent or received?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Where can I find all the PRESSIE gifts I sent or received?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;You can find all the gift records from your Profile page ! Just tap on your profile picture on the Menu list.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">You can find all the gift records from your Profile page ! Just tap on your profile picture on the Menu list.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;What if I decide to cancel a gift I sent, is that possible?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">What if I decide to cancel a gift I sent, is that possible?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;All sales are final. However, we accept refund request on a case by case basis. You can cancel gifts within 7 days of purchase (if the recipient hasn\'t collected it yet) by emailing joy@pressie.com.hk using your register email with the Gift Code, we\'ll reply within 2 business days.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">All sales are final. However, we accept refund request on a case by case basis. You can cancel gifts within 7 days of purchase (if the recipient hasn\'t collected it yet) by emailing joy@pressie.com.hk using your register email with the Gift Code, we\'ll reply within 2 business days.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Is there any charges for gift refund or return?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Is there any charges for gift refund or return?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Of course not ! If it is an item you received, we will arrange a third party courier to retrieve the gift.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Of course not ! If it is an item you received, we will arrange a third party courier to retrieve the gift.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How do I redeem a gift?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How do I redeem a gift?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Easy-peasy ! If the gift is by delivery, simply fill in the delivery form and we will have your gift delivered to you shortly. If you receive the gift in QR Code form, simply present the QR Code page to merchant and they will scan your Gift Card to redeem your gift. Beware of the Redeem Info section as some gifts may requires advance booking or redeem online.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Easy-peasy ! If the gift is by delivery, simply fill in the delivery form and we will have your gift delivered to you shortly. If you receive the gift in QR Code form, simply present the QR Code page to merchant and they will scan your Gift Card to redeem your gift. Beware of the Redeem Info section as some gifts may requires advance booking or redeem online.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;I have received a damaged item. What should I do?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">I have received a damaged item. What should I do?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;We are sorry to hear that ! Please send us an email at joy@pressie.com.hk , we will handle your problem very shortly! &quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">We are sorry to hear that ! Please send us an email at joy@pressie.com.hk , we will handle your problem very shortly!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Hong long is the gift valid for?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Hong long is the gift valid for?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;The gift expiration date can be vary. Gifts usually valid for a few months time except for those that only available on a specific date. You can refer to the expiration date of each gift which stated on the Gift Details page.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">The gift expiration date can be vary. Gifts usually valid for a few months time except for those that only available on a specific date. You can refer to the expiration date of each gift which stated on the Gift Details page.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;What if the gift is expired?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">What if the gift is expired?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;You would not be able to redeem your gift anymore if it is expired. So don\\u2019t let your friend\\u2019s goodwill go to waste!&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">You would not be able to redeem your gift anymore if it is expired. So don’t let your friend’s goodwill go to waste!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How should I do if I want to send more than one gift?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How should I do if I want to send more than one gift?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;That\'s easy ! All you need to do is to send us an email at joy@pressie.com.hk with your Mobile Phone No., your friend(s) Mobile Phone No. and the PRESSIE gift you want to send them with. We will reply to your email and help you through the process.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:771,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;4&quot;:[null,2,16773836],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">That\'s easy ! All you need to do is to send us an email at joy@pressie.com.hk with your Mobile Phone No., your friend(s) Mobile Phone No. and the PRESSIE gift you want to send them with. We will reply to your email and help you through the process.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;I\'ve got some opinions on the app, how can I share them?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">I\'ve got some opinions on the app, how can I share them?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;We\'re always welcome to opinions that can make PRESSIE better. If you have anything to share, email joy@pressie.com.hk&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">We\'re always welcome to opinions that can make PRESSIE better. If you have anything to share, email joy@pressie.com.hk</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;How can I work with PRESSIE?&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">How can I work with PRESSIE?</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Aww thanks for your support and we are very eager to be in a partnership. If you\'re interested to see your products or business featured, email info@pressie.gift.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:[null,0],&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">Aww thanks for your support and we are very eager to be in a partnership. If you\'re interested to see your products or business featured, email info@pressie.com.hk</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;I am thinki