 a very special Valentine’s Day</h1>\r\n<h2>LOVE · MUSIC · READ</h2>\r\nA Night of Soul Searching\r\n\r\nHmv has partnerd with social gifting app PRESSIE and HK Romance Dating to bring LOVE MUSIC READ. At this exclusive speed dating event, may a mutual love of music and literature be the start of something special.\r\n\r\n<b>13. Feb, 6-9pm</b>\r\nhmv Bar &amp; Restaurant\r\n4/F,Pearl City, 22-36 Paterson Street, CWB\r\nSpeeddating, Live Band, Buffet &amp; More\r\n\r\nTickets available on PRESSIE App\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 hidden-xs no-padding\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-3 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/qrcode-google.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/qrcode-apple.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 scroll_down\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/scroll_down.png\" alt=\"scroll down\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid promotion_body\">\r\n<div class=\"my-container\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 promotion_body_container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 no-padding\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/m1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 no-padding\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/m2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 no-padding\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/m3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h1>EVENT DETAILS</h1>\r\nThis event will take place in hmv\'s Pearl Square, Causeway Bay flagship store. Celebrating 90 years of providing world entertainment. Guests can enjoy a stunning visual and audio experience with live performances and more.\r\n\r\n<b>A Gentle Reminder for the Participants:</b> Don\'t forget to bring a gift (worth $100-$200) to exchange with that special someone. Still can\'t decide what to gift? Find a range of \'pick-us-all\' gifts plus get 10% off on your purchase. Keep checking our app for latest deals and exclusive products.\r\n\r\n<strong>Event Activities</strong>\r\n·<b>7pm-7:30pm</b> Free chatting,and first ice breaking games\r\n\r\n·<b>7:30pm-7:45pm</b> Live band performance\r\n\r\n·<b>7:45pm-8:30pm</b> Dinner and free chatting\r\n\r\n·<b>8:30pm-9pm</b> Second ice breaking games, play station games as a group(fastest group to complete all games are awarded)\r\n\r\n·<b>9pm-9:30pm</b> Gift exchange,free chatting, band performance,event conclusion\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h1>INSIDE THE APP</h1>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img id=\"app-link-img\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/seemore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 hr_line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row press_conf_wrap\">\r\n<h1>PRESS CONFERENCE</h1>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 hidden-xs love_mr_slider_wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"carousel-example-generic\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/sliderpc3.jpg\" alt=\"...\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/lovemusicread.html#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide=\"prev\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a><a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/lovemusicread.html#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide=\"next\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 slider_bottom_text\">\r\n<p class=\"love_music-teXT\"><b>We are excited that a lot of our media friends attended our hmv x PRESSIE x HKRD LOVE · MUSIC · READ speed dating press event on Feb 7, 2016.</b> We happily welcomed NLP tutor Nick and star hosts Anita and Yubi, who shared with us their specialist dating tips on clothing and more! We cannot wait for the main event on the 13th February now, and here are the tips that help you to prepare the speed dating!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 hr_line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row valentine_tips_wrap\">\r\n<h1>TIPS FOR VALENTINE\'S</h1>\r\n<div class=\"tabb\"><a>Tip 1</a> <a>Tip 2</a> <a>Tip 3</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 valentine_tips_text_wrap\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_one_Wrap\"><b>Relationship Tip 1 – Dating technique</b></h3>\r\nFirst impressions count, so it’s important to understand the other person’s type and break the ice appropriately to gain a deeper understanding. NLP tutor Nick taught us that you can understand the other person as three types of personality: observatory, listening, and sensory. When you know their type, you can then find suitable methods of communication to build an affinity.\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 no-padding\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th></th>\r\n<th>Observatory</th>\r\n<th>Listening</th>\r\n<th>Sensory</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Eye direction</th>\r\n<td>Changes between left and right</td>\r\n<td>Both ways</td>\r\n<td>It is usually lower than the center line, mostly in the lower right</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Pitch and speed of speech</th>\r\n<td>Fast speech, change, clear tone, expressed point</td>\r\n<td>Pay attention to rhythm, speed, detail</td>\r\n<td>Bass, depth, speed, interuptions and pauses</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Breathing</th>\r\n<td>Fast shallow breathing</td>\r\n<td>Balance breathing</td>\r\n<td>Deep breaths</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tips2\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_two_Wrap\"><b>Relationship Tip 2 – Mix &amp; Match to shape your body</b></h3>\r\nClothing is important to making a successful first impression. So with the help of two former star anchors, here’s tips of getting the right look.\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12 left-padding\">\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/icon_girls.png\" alt=\"\" /> GIRLS</h3>\r\n<h4>Neat and clean, shape and beautiful, let people to have a good impression.</h4>\r\nhigh waist line clothing to make you look taller, and pair with platform shoes or high heels to make the legs look longer Add a belt to hightlight the waist line and make the overall body scale slimmer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h4>Before &amp; After</h4>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_girlsbefore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_girlsafter.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 left-padding\">\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/icon_guys.png\" alt=\"\" /> GUYS</h3>\r\nClean and simple - you can wear high color contrast clothing between the inter and outter clothes to create the freshness and clean\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_shorty.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Shorty Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.Need to be Fit:</b> too loose will look shorter, too tight will look thin\r\n\r\n<b>b.Pick the straight cut,</b>there is a straight line lengthening effect, fabrics should be hard a little, not too soft or heavy\r\n\r\n<b>c.Color, preferably the same color pants, shirt and trousers</b> or inside the same color, looks will have the effect of lengthening\r\n\r\n<b>d.Clothes near the neckline position of the face,</b> the choice of color for their own, people\'s attention will shift up\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_tall.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Tall Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.If relatively thin, do not wear dark clothes,</b>it’s because the visual effect of contraction will become more and more thin\r\n\r\n<b>b.Avoid wearing checks,</b> try to choose stripes shirt\r\n\r\n<b>c.Avoid ultra-narrow or wide pants,</b>straight jeans choice\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_overweight.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Slightly Overweight Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.</b>Avoid large patterns\r\n\r\n<b>b.</b>Cool colors\r\n\r\n<b>c.</b>Wide belt use\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h4>Before &amp; After</h4>\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_guysbefore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http:/