or tone is not good for them as well.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Winter Type</b>\r\nGeneraly has their own characters, eyes are sharp contrast between black and white, fair and dim skin color, dark redish hair color. This type of people are more suitable for strong contrast color to reveil the personality like pure red, blue, yellow, green, black, white, gray, etc. For those who gives a cool image when they are in black are usaully winter-type people.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Gift a very special Valentine’s Day / LOVE · MUSIC · READ','','inherit','closed','closed','','531-revision-v1','','','2016-04-19 06:33:24','2016-04-19 06:33:24','',531,'http://www.pressie.com.hk/531-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(538,1,'2016-04-19 06:33:39','2016-04-19 06:33:39','<div class=\"container-fluid lmr_top_container\" >\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\" style=\"width:60% !important\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 left-padding hmv_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-xs-12 left-padding imr_wrap\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/hmv2.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"hmv_img_cont\">Gift a very special Valentine’s Day</h1>\r\n<h2>LOVE · MUSIC · READ</h2>\r\nA Night of Soul Searching\r\n\r\nHmv has partnerd with social gifting app PRESSIE and HK Romance Dating to bring LOVE MUSIC READ. At this exclusive speed dating event, may a mutual love of music and literature be the start of something special.\r\n\r\n<b>13. Feb, 6-9pm</b>\r\nhmv Bar &amp; Restaurant\r\n4/F,Pearl City, 22-36 Paterson Street, CWB\r\nSpeeddating, Live Band, Buffet &amp; More\r\n\r\nTickets available on PRESSIE App\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 hidden-xs no-padding\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-3 col-lg-offset