b class=\"tips_number\">Spring Type</b>\r\nBrightful eyes, brown pupil, skin color is usually ivory or light beige, pink cheeks, light hair color. Spring-type people are more suitable for the brightful and sweet colors. Wearing black and dark colors will make spring-type people become dim; therefore, they should choose soft and warm colors, such as yellow, orange, the color can not be too old or too dark.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Summer Type</b>\r\nBlack or dark brown pupil, fair skin, rosy cheeks, dark hair color. Such people should not wear black, because dark colors will destroy their soft and elegant image, they are more suitable for wearing clothes in light and cold colors such as light blue, light yellow, white, light gray and so on.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Autumn Type</b>\r\nDark pupil usually black or dark brown, dim and yellow skin, not much redish in cheek, dark brown hair, overall speaking it’s quite balance and low profile. Autumn type people usually give mature impression; therefore, they are more suitable for calm and warm colors, such as yellow tone, dark red tone, green and brown tone, it is best not to wear the color that is too much in contrast, and cold color tone is not good for them as well.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Winter Type</b>\r\nGeneraly has their own characters, eyes are sharp contrast between black and white, fair and dim skin color, dark redish hair color. This type of people are more suitable for strong contrast color to reveil the personality like pure red, blue, yellow, green, black, white, gray, etc. For those who gives a cool image when they are in black are usaully winter-type people.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Gift a very special Valentine’s Day / LOVE · MUSIC · READ','','inherit','closed','closed','','531-revision-v1','','','2016-04-19 06:34:04','2016-04-19 06: