\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/insapp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\"><img id=\"app-link-img\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/seemore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 hr_line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row press_conf_wrap\">\r\n<h1>PRESS CONFERENCE</h1>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 hidden-xs love_mr_slider_wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"carousel-example-generic\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/sliderpc3.jpg\" alt=\"...\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/lovemusicread.html#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide=\"prev\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a><a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/lovemusicread.html#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide=\"next\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 slider_bottom_text\">\r\n<p class=\"love_music-teXT\"><b>We are excited that a lot of our media friends attended our hmv x PRESSIE x HKRD LOVE · MUSIC · READ speed dating press event on Feb 7, 2016.</b> We happily welcomed NLP tutor Nick and star hosts Anita and Yubi, who shared with us their specialist dating tips on clothing and more! We cannot wait for the main event on the 13th February now, and here are the tips that help you to prepare the speed dating!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 hr_line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row valentine_tips_wrap\">\r\n<h1>TIPS FOR VALENTINE\'S</h1>\r\n<div class=\"tabb\"><a>Tip 1</a> <a>Tip 2</a> <a>Tip 3</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 valentine_tips_text_wrap\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_one_Wrap\"><b>Relationship Tip 1 – Dating technique</b></h3>\r\nFirst impressions count, so it’s important to understand the other person’s type and break the ice appropriately to gain a deeper understanding. NLP tutor Nick taught us that you can understand the other person as three types of personality: observatory, listening, and sensory. When you know their type, you can then find suitable methods of communication to build an affinity.\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 no-padding\">\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th></th>\r\n<th>Observatory</th>\r\n<th>Listening</th>\r\n<th>Sensory</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Eye direction</th>\r\n<td>Changes between left and right</td>\r\n<td>Both ways</td>\r\n<td>It is usually lower than the center line, mostly in the lower right</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Pitch and speed of speech</th>\r\n<td>Fast speech, change, clear tone, expressed point</td>\r\n<td>Pay attention to rhythm, speed, detail</td>\r\n<td>Bass, depth, speed, interuptions and pauses</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"row\">Breathing</th>\r\n<td>Fast shallow breathing</td>\r\n<td>Balance breathing</td>\r\n<td>Deep breaths</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tips2\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_two_Wrap\"><b>Relationship Tip 2 – Mix &amp; Match to shape your body</b></h3>\r\nClothing is important to making a successful first impression. So with the help of two former star anchors, here’s tips of getting the right look.\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12 left-padding\">\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/icon_girls.png\" alt=\"\" /> GIRLS</h3>\r\n<h4>Neat and clean, shape and beautiful, let people to have a good impression.</h4>\r\nhigh waist line clothing to make you look taller, and pair with platform shoes or high heels to make the legs look longer Add a belt to hightlight the waist line and make the overall body scale slimmer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h4>Before &amp; After</h4>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_girlsbefore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_girlsafter.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 left-padding\">\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/icon_guys.png\" alt=\"\" /> GUYS</h3>\r\nClean and simple - you can wear high color contrast clothing between the inter and outter clothes to create the freshness and clean\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_shorty.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Shorty Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.Need to be Fit:</b> too loose will look shorter, too tight will look thin\r\n\r\n<b>b.Pick the straight cut,</b>there is a straight line lengthening effect, fabrics should be hard a little, not too soft or heavy\r\n\r\n<b>c.Color, preferably the same color pants, shirt and trousers</b> or inside the same color, looks will have the effect of lengthening\r\n\r\n<b>d.Clothes near the neckline position of the face,</b> the choice of color for their own, people\'s attention will shift up\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_tall.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Tall Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.If relatively thin, do not wear dark clothes,</b>it’s because the visual effect of contraction will become more and more thin\r\n\r\n<b>b.Avoid wearing checks,</b> try to choose stripes shirt\r\n\r\n<b>c.Avoid ultra-narrow or wide pants,</b>straight jeans choice\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-xs-12 talll_img\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_overweight.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tall_over_waight_wrap\">\r\n<h3>Slightly Overweight Guys</h3>\r\n<b>a.</b>Avoid large patterns\r\n\r\n<b>b.</b>Cool colors\r\n\r\n<b>c.</b>Wide belt use\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h4>Before &amp; After</h4>\r\n<img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_guysbefore.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_guysafter.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tips3\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-xs-12\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/hmv_imge/img_colourcommunication.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-xs-12 \">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_three_Wrap\"><b>Relationship Tip 3: Color Communication</b></h3>\r\nApart from communication and body shape, your appearance can help to gain good impression as well. Finding the right color tone that brings out the best of you can help to attract the eye balls from the opposite sex.\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">1. Your skin color is:</h3>\r\n<p class=\"tips_NUMBER_WRAP\"><b>A.</b> Fair - Go to 2</p>\r\n<p class=\"tips_NUMBER_WRAP\"><b>B.</b> Tan - Go to 3</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 tips_NUMBER_WRAP\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">2. When you are wearing black clothing but without make-up on,</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> your skin looks flawlessly fair - Go to 5\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> you look a bit tired - Go to 6\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">3. More suitable for formal wear in:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Dark colors (black, dark grey, coffee) - Go to 6\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Light colors (white, light grey, milk white) - Go to 4\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">4. When going to sunbath, your skin will:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Immediate get tan - Go to 8\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Turn red but will change back to normal - Go to o7\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">5. The color of your eyes is:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> high Black and white contrast - Go to 9\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> relatively soft - Go to 7\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">6. Your suitable lipstick color is</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Coral pink（Orange） - Go to 4\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Rose pink (Red) - Go to 7\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">7. You are more suitable for accessories that are in:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Silver - Go to 12\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Gold - Go to 10\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">8. Your personality are more skewed toward to:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Gorgeous and lively - Go to 5\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Cool and wise- Go to 12\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">9. Do you think you’re suitable to wearing colorful patterns?</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Yes - Winter Type\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> No - Autumn Type\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">10. Pupil color is:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Dark brown or black - Go to 12\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Partial bright brown - Go to 11\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">11. Fingernail color is:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Rose red - Fuchsia - Summer Type\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Peach red - Orange red -  Spring Type\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_number\">12. Your outlook is more:</h3>\r\n<b>A.</b> Mature - Go to 9\r\n\r\n<b>B.</b> Teenage - Go to 11\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 result_wrap\">\r\n<h2>RESULTS:</h2>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Spring Type</b>\r\nBrightful eyes, brown pupil, skin color is usually ivory or light beige, pink cheeks, light hair color. Spring-type people are more suitable for the brightful and sweet colors. Wearing black and dark colors will make spring-type people become dim; therefore, they should choose soft and warm colors, such as yellow, orange, the color can not be too old or too dark.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Summer Type</b>\r\nBlack or dark brown pupil, fair skin, rosy cheeks, dark hair color. Such people should not wear black, because dark colors will destroy their soft and elegant image, they are more suitable for wearing clothes in light and cold colors such as light blue, light yellow, white, light gray and so on.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Autumn Type</b>\r\nDark pupil usually black or dark brown, dim and yellow skin, not much redish in cheek, dark brown hair, overall speaking it’s quite balance and low profile. Autumn type people usually give mature impression; therefore, they are more suitable for calm and warm colors, such as yellow tone, dark red tone, green and brown tone, it is best not to wear the color that is too much in contrast, and cold color tone is not good for them as well.</p>\r\n<p class=\"results_font_color\"><b class=\"tips_number\">Winter Type</b>\r\nGeneraly has their own characters, eyes are sharp contrast between black and white, fair and dim skin color, dark redish hair color. This type of people are more suitable for strong contrast color to reveil the personality like pure red, blue, yellow, green, black, white, gray, etc. For those who gives a cool image when they are in black are usaully winter-type people.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Gift a very special Valentine’s Day / LOVE · MUSIC · READ','','inherit','closed','closed','','531-revision-v1','','','2016-04-19 06:50:01','2016-04-19 06:50:01','',531,'http://www.pressie.com.hk/531-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(542,1,'2016-04-19 06:51:20','2016-04-19 06:51:20','','easter-main','','inherit','open','closed','','easter-main','','','2016-04-19 06:51:20','2016-04-19 06:51:20','',540,'http://www.pressie.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/easter-main.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(543,1,'2016-04-19 06:51:27','2016-04-19 06:51:27','<div class=\"container-fluid k11_top_container hiphop_top_container\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div clas