ecial name engraving.</b></div>\r\n<span class=\"activity1_small_text\"><b>Obellery:</b> The studio aims to promote the handicraft of contemporary, out-of-the-ordinary jewelry that bring out your personality.Workshops are suitable for family,friends and couple.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n<h2 class=\"activity3\">Activity 3</h2>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 no-padding\">\r\n<div id=\"carousel-example-generic2\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/image/image_k11/atum_1.jpg\" alt=\"...\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/k11.html#carousel-example-generic2\" data-slide=\"prev\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a><a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/k11.html#carousel-example-generic2\" data-slide=\"next\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 k11_text_wrap\">\r\n<h3 class=\"tips_three_Wrap\"><b>ATUM Set Dinner</b></h3>\r\nWatch closely as the <b>two culinary masters craft your dinner into pieces of art.</b> The dinner featuring nouvelle cuisine will end on an elegant note with the Rose Flower Performance.\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xs-12 pressie_exclusive\"><b>PRESSIE <i>Exclusive</i></b>\r\nEnjoy the fun \"test of love\" as your special one <b>mixes the Iced Wild Berry Tea trying to mak the color the same as yours!</b></div>\r\n<span class=\"activity1_small_text\"><b>ATUM:</b> We admire ATUM for making every dish with dedication and presenting it with a unique artistic flair. The one-of-a-kind desserts will surely make your day.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12 hr_line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"