time with their children.  To fulfill the deepest wish of your Mom, here are three unique activities that will make the most memorable Mother’s Day ever, plus three WOW gifts that will surely give her more joy!\r\n<h5><b>Activity 1: Mother-Daughter Yoga Class with Jessica</b></h5>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Have you ever dreamt of having a more intimate relationship with Mom?  This Mother-Daughter Yoga Class will help - especially if you find talking to Mom difficult.  All you need to do is breathe and enjoy a quiet hour of foundational yoga do with your Mom (no talking is necessary!).  Jessica, a certified yoga teacher, will teach Partner Yoga poses that you and Mom can do together to enhance each other\'s stretch.  To help you remember this peaceful hour together, you will each take home a beautifully designed silver chakra necklace at the end of the class.</span>\r\n<h5><b>Activity 2: </b><b>Leather Flower Making Workshop @Els</b></h5>\r\nDo you want to make something with Mom that she can keep forever?  If so, this beautiful, 100% handcrafted leather flower is your perfect choice.  Let the lines and crinkles on this classy leather flower tell a story of your unwithering, long-lasting love for your Mom!  Besides placing it on the table, your Mom can also pin it onto her shopping bag or something she uses frequently to make it a constant reminder of your love.\r\n<h5><b>Activity 3: Lollipop Making Workshop @HeyCandy</b></h5>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What childhood memories with your Mom do you miss?  Whatever they are, let this lollipop making workshop transport you both back to those fond moments!  Apart from choosing flavours and colors you like, you can also include a love message on your lollipop for Mom - adding that extra bit of sweetness coming from your heart!</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/2016-04-21.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649 size-full\" src=\"http://www.pressie.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/2016-04-21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" /></a>\r\n<h5><b>WOW Gift 1: </b><b>Flower Arrangement Workshop @Xen Fleurs</b></h5>\r\nOne-of-a-kind, isn\'t it?  This is definitely one of the most elegant surprises you can give to your flower enthusiast at home this Mother’s Day!  Let McQueens certified florist Xenia custom make the most unique, utterly gorgeous flower art that can stand on your Mom\'s table!\r\n<h5><b>WOW Gift 2: Mom’s Extra Hand @ iRobot</b></h5>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What’s a better way to say thank you to the Best Housewife of The World than this smart little mopping robot that will rid her the aches and pains from dragging a vacuum cleaner around?  Give her this “extra hand” which efficiently cover every tight corners and small spaces in the house!  </span>\r\n<h5><b>WOW Gift 3: Sweet Talk @ La Fievre Chocolate</b></h5>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you have words in your heart you\'ve always found it hard to express to Mom?  Why not let these custom word-imprinted chocolate cubes speak for you.  No matter it’s “I love you” or “You’re the best”, these exquisite handmade chocolates will carry your deepest thoughts in the most straightforward but heartfelt way.</span>','6 Most Heartfelt Mother’s Day Surprises 2016','','inherit','closed','closed','','573-revision-v1','','','2016-04-21 10:17:51','2016-04-21 10:17:51','',573,'http://www.pressie.com.hk/573-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(651,1,'2016-04-21 11:28:54','2016-04-21 11:28:54','<h1>Make Someone Feel Special Today</h1>\r\n<h5>xdfnxdfnxdfxdfxdfxdfxd</h5>','Banner','','inherit','closed','closed','','319-revision-v1','','','2016-04-21 11:28:54','2016-04-21 11:28:54','',319,'http://www.pressie.com.hk/319-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(652,1,'2016-04-21 11:30:56','2016-04-21 11:30:56','<h1>Make Someone Feel Special Today</h1>\n<h>Loren specializes in hand-crafted premium denim that is truly one-of-a-kind,</h5>','Banner','','inherit